            <li>🔡 <strong>Improved Chat Reliability</strong>: Resolved several underlying issues to ensure that every chat session opens predictably and reliably every time.</li>
            <li>✨ <strong>Sidebar Enhancements</strong>: Added a live session counter and improved the sidebar visibility for better insight into your active conversations.</li>
            <li>🪟 <strong>Window Behavior Polish</strong>: Refined how the app transitions between full-screen and accessory modes to provide a smoother, more intuitive experience.</li>
